folder: Wiman Place & Clifton Avenue, Staten Island, NY
text:
(1) Wilman Place (left, not seen), east side, north of Clifton Ave. This house belonged to C. O'Connor (1874 map), Brennan (1898 to 1907 maps), and later (1917 map) to Emily McAndrews. The view is northward from Clifton Ave.

February 25, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) A view of the east side of the house as viewed westward along Sylva Lane from near Edgewater Street.

February 25, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.

(3) A distant view of the house in a northwesterly direction.

February 25, 1931.

P. S. Sperr.
